Packages 
Package Description
clients
Provides the classes necessary to represent any entity on the client side of the execution.
configurations
Provides the classes necessary to configure the executions.
entities
Provides the classes necessary to create a set of characters needed to complete a horse race scenario.
hippodrome
Provides the classes necessary to create an environment needed to complete a horse race scenario.
hippodrome.actions
Provides the extra classes necessary to create actions of a horse race scenario.
hippodrome.responses
Provides the classes necessary to answer and represent any response from a entity state change, in order to well update the current state of a given thread's execution.
hippodrome.rollfilm
Provides the classes which saves a snapshot of both entities at stake and the race.
lib.logging
Provides the classes necessary to Log the activity on the servers and entities.
registry
Provides the classes needed to connect and register hippodrome regions along a RMI registry.
server
Provides the classes necessary to represent any hippodrome region on the server side of the execution.
